to prove to you.

41:40.932 --> 41:42.167
You got that?

41:46.037 --> 41:47.172
This doesn't mean anything.

41:47.205 --> 41:48.173
You get that?

41:48.206 --> 41:50.542
I don't like you.

41:50.576 --> 41:51.910
Yeah, see, uh...

41:51.943 --> 41:53.545
